  "page": "Nevio Narratys",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\"><img alt=\"Pentos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/50px-Pentos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/75px-Pentos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/100px-Pentos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Prince</span><br />Nevio Narratys</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\"><img alt=\"Pentos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/50px-Pentos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/75px-Pentos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/100px-Pentos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentoshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Nevio Narratys</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nevio_Narratys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Nevio was chosen as Prince during the latest war between <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> over <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a>, which ended in <a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a>. He was the fifth prince chosen in the span of that single year, for the war had been a disaster for Pentos, where <a href=\"/index.php/Magisters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magisters\">Magisters</a> sacrifice the Prince should a crop be lost or a war be lost. Nevio convinced the magisters to sue for peace after a rare victory - one that is rumored to have been purchased by Nevio himself through bribery. In these peace accords Pentos was forced to abolish slavery and withdraw from the slave trade.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nevio_Narratys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities: Pentos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404143045\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.334 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 406/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10429/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4670/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 333/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 612/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.42 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  325.205      1 -total\n 96.48%  313.758      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.75%  311.386      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.26%   39.856     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.46%   11.257      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.60%    5.204      1 Template:Date\n  1.43%    4.637      1 Template:Ref\n  0.83%    2.697      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.42%    1.351      1 Template:References\n  0.27%    0.886      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19461-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404143044 and revision id 286723\n -->\n",
